OL,3,CNI public services 'at risk of
OL,4,Ccollapse'
OL,6,FA group of public service bodies
OL,7,Facross Northern Ireland have warned
OL,8,Fthat new UK Government National
OL,9,FInsurance Contribution and Minimum
OL,10,FWage increases will have an immediate
OL,11,Fimpact on patients and leaving them at
OL,12,F'risk of collapse.'
OL,14,FOn Monday, Community Pharmacists,
OL,15,FGeneral Practitioners, Dentists and
OL,16,FOptometrists called on the Health
OL,17,FMinister and the Northern Ireland
OL,18,FExecutive for immediate financial
OL,19,Fsupport.
