OL,3,CNI public services 'at risk of
OL,4,Ccollapse'
OL,6,FIn January during a Stormont's Health
OL,7,FCommitee, GPs first warned of the
OL,8,Fimpacts of the budget pressures and
OL,9,Fhave now reissued this message.
OL,11,FThis comes as the amount which
OL,12,Femployers will have to pay in National
OL,13,FInsurance rose on Sunday from 13.8% to
OL,14,F15% of employees' wages.
OL,16,FThe four bodies have stated the impact
OL,17,Fof these additional overheads will be
OL,18,Fan inevitable reduction in opening
OL,19,Fhours, cuts to staffing levels and
OL,20,Freduced access to patient care.
