OL,3,CNI public services 'at risk of
OL,4,Ccollapse'
OL,6,FThe Health Minister has confirmed the
OL,7,Fnew cost impacts could cost the
OL,8,Findependent sector #36.5m annually.
OL,10,FSpeaking at Stormont today he said:
OL,11,F"These are really serious challenges,
OL,12,Fto continue to deliver health care at
OL,13,Fthe level we are delivering it at."
OL,15,FHe continued: "I'm working with
OL,16,Fofficials to see what we can do to try
OL,17,Fand mitigate that."
