OL,6,FNow the public are being warned to
OL,7,Fexpect a reduction in opening hours
OL,8,Fand staff levels and longer waiting
OL,9,Ftimes.
OL,11,FUnlike hospitals or health trusts
OL,12,Fwhich fund staff costs through
OL,13,Fnational health service pay
OL,14,Fagreements, these practitioners are
OL,15,Fnot shielded from the latest revenue-
OL,16,Fraising as many of these practitioners
OL,17,Foperate as small businesses and are
OL,18,Fresponsible for their own wage bills.
