OL,6,F"The scope for each of us to raise
OL,7,Fadditional revenue is extremely
OL,8,Flimited and we would not want patients
OL,9,Fhaving to pay more when their own
OL,10,Ffinances will be similarly stretched.
OL,12,F"We call on the Health Minister and
OL,13,Fthe Executive to intervene immediately
OL,14,Fand provide the mitigation and support
OL,15,Fneeded to offset these latest cost
OL,16,Fincreases we now face."
