OL,6,FChief Executive of Community Pharmacy
OL,7,FNI, Gerard Greene, said, "In the
OL,8,Fprivate sector, businesses can often
OL,9,Foffset such cost increases by raising
OL,10,Fthe prices of their goods and services.
OL,12,F"Community pharmacies do not have this
OL,13,Foption. Unlike the health service,
OL,14,Fthey are not shielded from these
OL,15,Fincreases."
